{"word":"ἄμμορος","slug":"ἄμμορος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄμμορος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:poetically'>poet.</a> for <el>ἄμορος, ἄμοιρος</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>without share of</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>:—<i>free from, without</i>, <el>ὠδίνων</el> <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>unhappy</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}